This repository is vim config file
==================================

I'm looking for a good configuration that make me feel like 
I can fly over my keyboard with vim, whereas I save the 
history of all the changes.

Dependences
===========

  + vim-plug 

Architecture
============

Attempt to keep one reason of change.

  .
  ├── init.vim
  │
  ├── plugin
  │   │
  │   ├── fzf.vim
  │   ├── vim-go.vim
  │   │
  │   └── own
  │       │
  │       ├── keybinds.vim
  │       ├── statusline.vim
  │       .
  │
  ├── README
  │

  plugin: in here I put plugins configurations.

  plugin/own: in here I put all of my own "plugins" e.g., 
  my own statusline or my own keybinds. 

  why plugin folder? see commit 5564a18.

